@startuml
title lizard-prod-and-tests (metrics/generic/cyclomatic-complexity/lizard-prod-and-tests)
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

node "Docker container\nlizard-prod-and-tests" as container
folder "/app\n(src mounted RO)" as app
database "/results\n(JSONL)" as results
component "Toolchain\n(as per Dockerfile)" as tool

app --> container : scan files
container --> tool : run metric tool
tool --> results : emit JSONL rows\n(project, metric, tool, variant,...)

note right of results
Output filename pattern:
<project>-<timestamp>-<metric>-<tool>-<variant>.jsonl
end note

@enduml
